!Sample_extract_protocol_ch1 = scRNAseq libraries (5Â´ gene expression library GEX, T cell receptor enriched library VDJ, and surface protein library containing the TotalSeq-C CITE-seq antibodies) were prepared using the Chromium Single Cell Immune Profiling kit (10x Genomics, v1.1) according to the manufacturerâs instructions. The generated scRNAseq libraries were sequenced using a total of 100 cycles (paired end reads) with a NovaSeq 6000 S2 flow cell (Illumina).
!Sample_description = Library name: Patient P097_Treg_mrna
!Sample_description = polyA RNA
